{"tid":236543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[抒情po]肥妹成情場勝利組黑馬　必勝要訣︰我走內涵路線","createTime":"2017-05-09T20:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T08:04:38.000Z","uid":80900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8bd463e17bf7e7c08521bba2d686a2064ec015","tid":236543,"uid":80900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/46868?utm_content=bufferfe7d4&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F46868%3Futm_content%3Dbufferfe7d4%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7e8f262a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/46868?utm_content=bufferfe7d4&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\nQuote左啲內容:<br />\n<br />\nT小姐的拍拖次數，多得她也數不來，由四年級開始初戀，至今已有超過20個男朋友，人數差不多足夠「擺兩圍」，當中有散拖對象、有認真發展的、也有結婚對象。在她的故事中，「肥」與「愛情」是重要關鍵詞，兩者密不可分。<br />\n雖然有無數男生單憑她的外表而討厭她，但她也有很多純友誼的異性朋友，更有不少男士追求。當然，她也會主動出擊追求男生，成功率高達7至8成，她也承認，相比外貌討好的女生，她追求男生會感到較吃力。雖然如此，由初戀開始，她最長只經歷過一年多的單身空窗期，歷屆前男友，有校草級靚仔；有不靚仔；有富二代；也有窮困小子，但極具上進心；當中也有幾個「渣男」。<br />\n<br />\n點解人地成百幾二百磅都拍過廿幾次拖，最長只經歷過一年多的單身空窗期，而我只係一個小小既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好勵志既同時都好灰....點解會咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86534870d0eb9fe6273bd672f3713589898cbb90","tid":236543,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T20:57:26.000Z","msg":"不了,叫雞好過"},{"pid":"0ad711e37de9b8ab34a5fb99525501eb5cab00f1","tid":236543,"uid":50483,